S Salute (AM-294)|Salute]]'', ''[[USS Saunter|Saunter]]'', ''[[USS Scout (AM-296)|Scout]]'', ''[[USS Scrimmage|Scrimmage]]'', ''[[USS Sentry (AM-299)|Sentry]]''\n: 2 minelayers: ''[[USS Preble (DM-20)|Preble]]'', ''[[USS Breese (DM-18)|Breese]]''\n: 26 [[auxiliary motor minesweeper]]s\n: 1 [[harbour defence motor launch]]: {{flagdeco|Australia}} ''1074''\n\n===== Beach Demolition Group (Task Group 77.6) =====\nLt. Commander C.C. Morgan, USNR<br>\nEmbarking [[Underwater Demolition Team]]s 3, 4, 5, 6, 8, 9, 10\n: 11 destroyer transports: ''[[USS Talbot (DD-114)|Talbot]]'', ''[[USS Manley (DD-74)|Manley]]'', ''[[USS Goldsborough (DD-188)|Goldsborough]]'', ''[[USS Kane (DD-235)|Kane]]'', ''[[USS Brooks|Brooks]]'', ''[[USS Belknap (DD-251)|Belknap]]'', ''[[USS Overton|Overton]]'', ''[[USS Humphreys|Humphreys]]'', ''[[USS Rathburne (DD-113)|Rathburne]]'', ''[[USS George E. Badger|George E. Badger]]'', ''[[USS Clemson (DD-186)|Clemson]]''\n\n=== Amphibious Assault Units ===\n\n==== Northern Attack Force (Task Force 78) ====\n{{multiple image\n | direction = horizontal\n | width = 190\n | header = Amphibious force commander for Northern Landing Area\n | image1 = Daniel_E._Barbey2.JPG\n | caption1 = Rear Adm. Daniel E. Barbey\n}}\nRear Admiral [[Daniel E. Barbey]] in amphibious command ship ''[[USS Blue Ridge|Blue Ridge]]<br>\nEmbarking [[File:X_Corps_SSI.gif|28px]] '''[[X Corps (United States)|X Army Corps]]'''\n\n[[File:USS_Gunston_Hall;10120515.jpg|220px|thumb|Landing ship dock ''Gunston Hall]]''\n[[File:World_War_2_USCG_PC.jpg|220px|thumb|Steel-hulled sub chaser]]\n[[File:USS_James_O%27Hara_APA-90.jpg|220px|thumb|Attack transport ''James O'Hara'']]\n[[File:USS_LST-568.jpg|220px|thumb|Landing ship tank]]\n\n'''Palo Attack Group (Task Group 78.1)'''<br>\nRear Admiral Barbey<br>\nEmbarking [[File:24_Infantry_Division_SSI.png|28px]] [[24th Infantry Division (United States)|24th Infantry (\"Taro\") Division]] (Left beaches)\n: Transport Unit (Capt. T.B. Brittain)\n:: Transport Division 24 (Capt. Brittain)\n::: 4 [[attack transport]]s: ''[[USS DuPage (APA-41)|DuPage]]'', ''[[USS Fuller (AP-14)|Fuller]]'', ''[[USS Elmore|Elmore]]'', ''[[USS Wayne (APA-54)|Wayne]]''\n::: 1 transport: ''[[USS John Land (AP-167)|John Land]]''\n::: 1 attack cargo ship: ''[[USS Aquarius|Aquarius]]''\n::: 1 [[landing ship dock]]: ''[[USS Gunston Hall (LSD-5)|Gunston Hall]]''\n:: Transport Division 6 (Capt. H.D. Baker)\n::: 3 attack transports: ''[[USS Fayette|Fayette]]'', ''[[USS Ormsby|Ormsby]]'', ''[[USS Leedstown (APA-56)|Leedstown]]''\n::: 1 attack cargo ship: ''[[USS Titania|Titania]]''\n::: 1 cargo ship: ''[[USS Hercules (AK-41)|Hercules]]''\n::: 2 [[landing ship dock]]s: ''[[USS Epping Forest|Epping Forest]]'', ''[[USS Carter Hall (LSD-3)|Carter Hall]]''\n: Screen (Capt. Henry Crommelin)\n:: 4 destroyers (all [[Fletcher class destroyer|Fletcher-class]]): ''[[USS John Rodgers (DD-574)|John Rodgers]]'', ''[[USS Murray (DD-576)|Murray]]'', ''[[USS Harrison (DD-573)|Harrison]]'', ''[[USS McKee (DD-575)|McKee]]''\n: Control and Close Support Unit (Capt. N.D. Brantly)\n:: 4 [[submarine chaser]]s: 3 steel hull, 1  wooden hull\n:: 16 landing craft infantry: 9 [[Landing Craft Infantry|standard]], 5 [[Landing Craft Infantry#LCI(R) - Rocket|rocket]], 2 [[Landing Craft Infantry#LCI(G) - Gunboat|gunboat]]\n:: 3 [[patrol craft escort]]\n:: 1 [[frigate#World War II|frigate]]\n:: 3 [[landing ship medium|landing ships medium]]\n:: 2 [[tugboat|fleet tugs]]: ''[[USS Apache (ATF-67)|Apache]]'', ''[[USS Quapaw|Quapaw]]''\n\n'''San Ricardo Attack Group (Task Group 78.2)'''<br>\nRear Admiral W.M. Fechteler in attack transport ''[[USS Fremont|Fremont]]''<br>\nEmbarking [[File:1st_Cavalry_Division_SSI_(full_color).svg|28px]] [[1st Cavalry Division (United States)|1st Cavalry Division]] (Right beaches)\n: Transport Unit (Capt. M.O. Carlson)\n:: Transport Division 32 (Capt. Carlson)\n::: 4 [[attack transport]]s: ''[[USS Harris|Harris]]'', ''[[USS Barnstable|Barnstable]]''\n::: 1 [[transport]]: ''Herald of the Morning''\n::: 1 [[attack cargo ship]]: ''[[USS Arneb|Arneb]]''\n::: 1 [[landing ship dock]]: ''[[USS White Marsh|White Marsh]]''\n:: Transport Division 20 (Capt. D.W. Loomis)\n::: 3 [[attack transport]]s: ''[[USS Leonard Wood|Leonard Wood]]'', ''[[USS P|Pierce]]'', ''[[USS James O'Hara|James O'Hara]]''\n::: 1 [[transport]]: ''[[USS La Salle (AP-102)|La Salle]]''\n::: 1 [[attack cargo ship]]: ''[[USS Electra (AKA-4)|Electra]]''\n::: 1 [[landing ship dock]]: ''[[USS Oak Hill (LSD-7)|Oak Hill]]''\n::: 9 [[landing ship medium|landing ships medium]]\n: Screen (Capt. A.E. Jarrell)\n:: 4 destroyers \n::: 3 [[Fletcher class destroyer|Fletcher-class]]: ''[[USS Fletcher (DD-445)|Fletcher]]'', ''[[USS Jenkins (DD-447)|Jenkins]]'', ''[[USS La Vallette (DD-448)|La Vallette]]''\n::: 1 [[Sims class destroyer|Sims-class]]: ''[[USS Anderson|Anderson]]''\n:: 1 [[tugboat|fleet tug]]: ''[[USS Sonoma|Sonoma]]''\n:: 8 landing craft infantry: 6 [[Landing Craft Infantry#LCI(R) - Rocket|rocket]], 2 [[Landing Craft Infantry#LCI(G) - Gunboat|gunboat]]\n:: 14 [[landing ship, tank|landing ships tank]]\n\n[[File:Aft_view_of_USS_Mississippi_(BB-41)_in_late_1942.jpg|230px|thumb|Battleship ''Mississippi'']]\n[[File:HMS_Ariadne_minelayer.jpg|220px|thumb|Minelayer HMS ''Ariadne'']]\n[[File:USS_Stack_%28DD-406%29.jpg|220px|thumb|Destroyer ''Stack'']]\n[[File:USS_Fletcher_(DD-445)_off_New_York,_1942.jpg|220px|thumb|right|Fletcher-class destroyer]]\n\n'''Fire Support Unit North'''<br>\nRear Admiral George L. Weyler\n: 3 old battleships: [[USS Mississippi (BB-41)|''Mississippi'']] (Capt. H.J. Redfield), [[USS Maryland (BB-46)|''Maryland'']] (Capt. H.J. Ray), [[USS West Virginia (BB-48)|''West Virginia'']] (Capt. H.V. Wiley)\n: 3 destroyers (all [[Fletcher class destroyer|Fletcher-class]]): ''[[USS Cony|Cony]]'', ''[[USS Aulick (DD-569)|Aulick]]'', ''[[USS Sigourney (DD-643)|Sigourney]]''\n\n'''Panaon Attack Group (Task Group 78.3)'''<br>\nRear Admiral A.D. Struble in ''[[USS Hughes (DD-410)|Hughes]]''<br>\nEmbarking 21st Regimental Combat Team / [[24th Infantry Division (United States)|24th Infantry Division]]\n: 1 destroyer ([[Sims class destroyer|Sims-class]]): ''[[USS Hughes (DD-410)|Hughes]]'' \n: 3 [[landing ship infantry|landing ships infantry]]: {{flagdeco|Australia}} [[HMAS Kanimbla (F23)|HMAS ''Kanimbla'']], {{flagdeco|Australia}} [[HMAS Manoora (F48)|HMAS ''Manoora'']],  {{flagdeco|Australia}} [[HMAS Westralia (F95)|HMAS ''Westralia'']]\n: 1 [[minelayer]]: {{flagdeco|Great Britain}} [[HMS Ariadne (M65)|HMS ''Ariadne'']]\n: 4 destroyers (all [[Fletcher class destroyer|Fletcher-class]]): ''[[USS Sigsbee|Sigsbee]]'', ''[[USS Ringgold (DD-500)|Ringgold]]'', ''[[USS Schroeder|Schroeder]]'', ''[[USS Dashiell|Dashiell]]''\n\n'''Dinagat Attack Group (Task Group 78.4)'''<br>\nRear Admiral Struble in ''[[USS Hughes (DD-410)|Hughes]]''<br>\nEmbarking [[6th Ranger Battalion]] and Co. B / 21st Infantry\n: 5 destroyer transports: ''[[USS Kilty|Kilty]]'', ''[[USS Schley (APD-14)|Schley]]'', ''[[USS Ward|Ward]]'', ''[[USS Herbert|Herbert]]'', ''[[USS Crosby|Crosby]]''\n: 1 fleet tug: ''[[USS Chickasaw (AT-83)|Chickasaw]]''\n: 2 destroyers (both [[Benham class destroyer|Benham-class]]): ''[[USS Lang (DD-399)|Lang]]'', ''[[USS Stack|Stack]]''\n: 2 [[frigate#World War II|frigate]]s: ''[[USS Gallup (PF-47)|Gallup]]'', ''[[USS Bisbee|Bisbee]]''\n\n'''Reinforcement Group One (Task Group 78.6)'''<br>\nCaptain S.P. Jenkins<br>\nArriving 22 October\n: 6 [[attack transport]]s: ''[[USS Crescent City|Crescent City]]'', ''[[USS Warren (APA-53)|Warren]]'', ''[[USS Windsor (APA-55)|Windsor]]'', ''[[USS Callaway|Callaway]]'', ''[[USS Leon|Leon]]'', ''[[USS Sumter (APA-52)|Sumter]]''\n: 1 [[transport]]: ''[[USS Storm King|Storm King]]''\n: 1 [[cargo ship]]: ''[[USS Jupiter (AK-43)|Jupiter]]''\n: 1 [[repair ship]]: ''[[USS Achilles (ARL-41)|Achilles]]''\n: 4 merchant ships\n: 32 [[landing ship, tank|landing ships tank]]\n: 12 [[landing craft infantry]]\n: Escort (Capt. E.A. Solomons)\n:: 4 destroyers\n::: 2 destroyers (both [[Sims class destroyer|Sims-class]]): ''[[USS Mustin (DD-413)|Mustin]]'', ''[[USS Morris (DD-417)|Morris]]''\n::: 2 destroyers (both [[Fletcher class destroyer|Fletcher-class]]: ''[[USS Stevens (DD-479)|Stevens]]'', ''[[USS Howorth|Howorth]]''\n:: 2 frigates (both [[Tacoma class frigate|Tacoma-class]]): ''[[USS Carson City (PF-50)|Carson City]]'', ''[[USS Burlington (PF-51)|Burlington]]''\n\n'''Reinforcement Group Two (Task Group 78.7)'''\n\n[[File:USS_Drayton_%28DD-366%29_underway_at_slow_speed_on_5_August_1936.jpg|220px|thumb|Destroyer ''Drayton'']]\n[[File:USS_Peoria_%28PF-67%29.jpg|220px|thumb|Tacoma-class frigate]]\n\nCaptain J.K.P. Ginder<br>\nArriving 24 October\n: 32 [[landing ship, tank|landing ships tank]]\n: 24 merchant ships\n: Escort (Capt. Ginder)\n:: 4 destroyers (all [[Fletcher class destroyer|Fletcher-class]]): ''[[USS Nicholas (DD-449)|Nicholas]]'', ''[[USS O'Bannon (DD-450)|O'Bannon]]'', ''[[USS Taylor (DD-468)|Taylor]]'', ''[[USS Hopewell (DD-681)|Hopewell]]''\n:: 2 frigates (both [[Tacoma class frigate|Tacoma-class]]): ''[[USS Muskogee|Muskogee]]'', ''[[USS San Pedro|San Pedro]]''\n\n'''Reinforcement Group Three (Task Group 78.9)'''<br>\nCommander J.L. Steinmetz, USCG<br>\nArriving 29 October\n: 62 [[landing ship, tank|landing ships tank]]\n: 19 merchant ships\n: Escort (Capt. W.M. Cole)\n:: 5 destroyers (all [[Mahan class destroyer|Mahan-class]]):  ''[[USS Mahan (DD-364)|Mahan]]'', ''[[USS Drayton (DD-366)|Drayton]]'', ''[[USS Lamson (DD-367)|Lamson]]'', ''[[USS Flusser (DD-368)|Flusser]]'', ''[[USS Smith (DD-378)|Smith]]''\n:: 4 frigates (all [[Tacoma class frigate|Tacoma-class]]): ''[[USS Eugene (PF-40)|Eugene]]'', ''[[USS El Paso (PF-41)|El Paso]]'', ''[[USS Van Buren (PF-42)|Van Buren]]'', ''[[USS Orange|Orange]]''\n\n==== Southern Attack Force (Task Force 79) ====\n{{multiple image\n | direction = horizontal\n | width = 160\n | header = Amphibious force commander for Southern Landing Area\n | image1 = Theodore Wilkinson 1944 small.jpg\n | caption1 = Vice Adm. Theodore S. Wilkinson \n}}\n{{multiple image\n | direction = horizontal\n | width = 220\n | header = Amphibious command ships\n | image1 = USS_Mount_Olympus_(AGC-8)_in_June_1944.jpg\n | caption1 = USS ''Mount Olympus''\n | image2 = USS_Appalachian_(AGC-1)_underway_off_New_York_on_18_October_1943.jpg\n | caption2 = USS ''Appalachian''\n}}\nVice Admiral [[Theodore S. Wilkinson]] in amphibious command ship ''[[USS Mount Olympus|Mount Olympus]]''<br>\nEmbarking [[File:XXIV_Corps_SSI.gif|28px]] '''[[XXIV Corps (United States)|XXIV Army Corps]]'''\n\n'''Attack Group \"Able\" (Task Group 79.1)'''<br>\nRear Admiral R.L. Conolly in amphibious command ship ''[[USS Appalachian|Appalachian]]''<br>\nEmbarking [[File:7th_Infantry_Division_DUI.svg|28px]] [[7th Infantry Division (United States)|7th Infantry \"Bayonet\" Division]] (Left beaches)\n\n: '''Transport Group \"Able\" (Task Group 79.3)'''\n: Capt. C.G. Richardson\n:: Transport Division 7 (Capt. Richardson)\n::: 3 [[attack transport]]s: ''[[USS Cavalier|Cavalier]]'', ''[[USS J. Franklin Bell|J. Franklin Bell]]'', ''[[USS Feland|Feland]]''\n::: 1 [[transport]]: ''Golden City''\n::: 1 [[attack cargo ship]]: ''[[USS Thuban|Thuban]]''\n::: 1 [[landing ship dock]]: ''[[USS Lindenwald|Lindenwald]]''\n:: Transport Division 30 (Capt. C.A. Mission)\n::: 3 [[attack transport]]s: ''[[USS Knox (APA-46)|Knox]]'', ''[[USS Calvert (AP-65)|Calvert]]'', ''[[USS Custer|Custer]]''\n::: 1 evacuation transport: ''[[USS Rixey|Rixey]]''\n::: 1 [[attack cargo ship]]: ''[[USS Chara|Chara]]''\n::: 1 [[landing ship dock]]: ''[[USS Ashland (LSD-1)|Ashland]]''\n:: Transport Division 38 (Capt. Charles Allen)\n::: 3 [[attack transport]]s: ''[[USS Lamar (APA-47)|Lamar]]'', ''[[USS Alpine|Alpine]]'', ''[[USS Heywood|Heywood]]''\n::: 2 [[transport]]s: ''[[USS Starlight|Starlight]]'', ''[[USS Monitor|Monitor]]''\n::: 1 [[attack cargo ship]]s: ''[[USS Alshain|Alshain]]''\