-44.jpg|220px|thumb|Grumman TBF Avenger torpedo bomber]]\n\nRear Admiral [[Clifton Sprague|Clifton A.F. Sprague]]\n: 6 escort carriers\n:: ''[[USS Fanshaw Bay|Fanshaw Bay]]'' (Capt. D.P. Johnson)\n::: ''Composite Squadron 68'' (Lt. Cmdr. R.S. Rogers)\n::: 16 [[FM-2 Wildcat]] fighters \n::: 12 [[TBM Avenger]] torpedo bombers\n:: ''[[USS St. Lo|St. Lo]]'' (Capt. F.J. McKenna)\n::: ''Composite Squadron 65'' (Lt. Cmdr. R.M. Jones, USMR)\n::: 17 [[FM-2 Wildcat]] fighters \n::: 12 [[TBM Avenger]] torpedo bombers\n:: ''[[USS White Plains|White Plains]]'' (Capt. D.J. Sullivan)\n::: ''Composite Squadron 4'' (Lt. E.R. Fickenscher)\n::: 16 [[FM-2 Wildcat]] fighters \n::: 12 [[TBM Avenger]] torpedo bombers\n:: ''[[USS Kalinin Bay|Kalinin Bay]]'' (Capt. T.B. Williamson)\n::: ''Composite Squadron 3'' (Lt. Cmdr. W.H. Keighley)\n::: 16 [[FM-2 Wildcat]] fighters \n::: &nbsp;&nbsp;1 [[TBF Avenger]], 11 [[TBM Avenger]] torpedo bombers\n: Carrier Division 26 (Rear Adm. R.A. Ofstie)\n:: ''[[USS Kitkun Bay|Kitkun Bay]]'' (Capt. J.P. Whitney)\n::: ''Composite Squadron 5'' (Cmdr. R.L. Fowler)\n::: 14 [[FM-2 Wildcat]] fighters \n::: 12 [[TBM Avenger]] torpedo bombers\n:: ''[[USS Gambier Bay|Gambier Bay]]'' (Capt. W.V.R. Vieweg)\n::: ''Composite Squadron 10'' (Lt. Cmdr. E.J. Huxtable)\n::: 18 [[FM-2 Wildcat]] fighters \n::: 12 [[TBM Avenger]] torpedo bombers\n: Screen (Cmdr. W.D. Thomas)\n:: 3 destroyers (all [[Fletcher class destroyer|Fletcher-class]]): [[USS Hoel (DD-533)|''Hoel'']], [[USS Heermann (DD-532)|''Heermann'']], [[USS Johnston (DD-557)|''Johnston'']]\n:: 4 destroyer escorts (all [[John C. Butler class destroyer escort|John C. Butler-class]]): [[USS Dennis|''Dennis'']], [[USS John C. Butler|''John C. Butler'']], [[USS Raymond (DE-341)|''Raymond'']], [[USS Samuel B. Roberts (DE-413)|''Samuel B. Roberts'']]\n\n===== Minesweeping and Hydrographic Group (Task Group 77.5) =====\n[[File:USS_Pursuit_%28AM_108%29.jpg|210px|thumb|Auk-class minesweeper]]\n[[File:StateLibQld_1_79147_Royal_Australian_Naval_ship_ML_1322_at_Colmslie_Naval_Base%2C_Brisbane%2C_ca._1944.jpg|210px|thumb|Australian harbour defence motor launch]]\nCommander W.R. Loud<br>\n: 1 frigate: {{flagdeco|Australia}} [[HMAS Gascoyne (K354)|HMAS ''Gascoyne'']]\n: 1 destroyer transport: ''[[USS Sands (APD-13)|Sands]]''\n: 7 fast minesweepers: ''[[USS Hovey|Hovey]]'', ''[[USS Southard|Southard]]'', ''[[USS Chandler (DD-206)|Chandler]]'', ''[[USS Long|Long]]'', ''[[USS Hamilton (DD-141)|Hamilton]]'', ''[[USS Howard (DD-179)|Howard]]'', ''[[USS Palmer (DD-161)|Palmer]]''\n: 12 minesweepers \n:: 7 [[Auk class minesweeper|Auk-class]]: ''[[USS Token|Token]]'', ''[[USS Tumult|Tumult]]'', ''[[USS Velocity (AM-128)|Velocity]]'', ''[[USS Requisite|Requisite]]'', ''[[USS Pursuit (AM-108)|Pursuit]]'', ''[[USS Revenge (AM-110)|Revenge]]'', ''[[USS Sage|Sage]]''\n:: 5 [[Admirable class minesweeper|Admirable-class]]: ''[[USS Salute (AM-294)|Salute]]'', ''[[USS Saunter|Saunter]]'', ''[[USS Scout (AM-296)|Scout]]'', ''[[USS Scrimmage|Scrimmage]]'', ''[[USS Sentry (AM-299)|Sentry]]''\n: 2 minelayers: ''[[USS Preble (DM-20)|Preble]]'', ''[[USS Breese (DM-18)|Breese]]''\n: 26 [[auxiliary motor minesweeper]]s\n: 1 [[harbour defence motor launch]]: {{flagdeco|Australia}} ''1074''\n\n===== Beach Demolition Group (Task Group 77.6) =====\nLt. Commander C.C. Morgan, USNR<br>\nEmbarking [[Underwater Demolition Team]]s 3, 4, 5, 6, 8, 9, 10\n: 11 destroyer transports: ''[[USS Talbot (DD-114)|Talbot]]'', ''[[USS Manley (DD-74)|Manley]]'', ''[[USS Goldsborough (DD-188)|Goldsborough]]'', ''[[USS Kane (DD-235)|Kane]]'', ''[[USS Brooks|Brooks]]'', ''[[USS Belknap (DD-251)|Belknap]]'', ''[[USS Overton|Overton]]'', ''[[USS Humphreys|Humphreys]]'', ''[[USS Rathburne (DD-113)|Rathburne]]'', ''[[USS George E. Badger|George E. Badger]]'', ''[[USS Clemson (DD-186)|Clemson]]''\n\n=== Amphibious Assault Units ===\n\n==== Northern Attack Force (Task Force 78) ====\n{{multiple image\n | direction = horizontal\n | width = 190\n | hea