rosby]]''\n: 1 fleet tug: ''[[USS Chickasaw (AT-83)|Chickasaw]]''\n: 2 destroyers (both [[Benham class destroyer|Benham-class]]): ''[[USS Lang (DD-399)|Lang]]'', ''[[USS Stack|Stack]]''\n: 2 [[frigate#World War II|frigate]]s: ''[[USS Gallup (PF-47)|Gallup]]'', ''[[USS Bisbee|Bisbee]]''\n\n'''Reinforcement Group One (Task Group 78.6)'''<br>\nCaptain S.P. Jenkins<br>\nArriving 22 October\n: 6 [[attack transport]]s: ''[[USS Crescent City|Crescent City]]'', ''[[USS Warren (APA-53)|Warren]]'', ''[[USS Windsor (APA-55)|Windsor]]'', ''[[USS Callaway|Callaway]]'', ''[[USS Leon|Leon]]'', ''[[USS Sumter (APA-52)|Sumter]]''\n: 1 [[transport]]: ''[[USS Storm King|Storm King]]''\n: 1 [[cargo ship]]: ''[[USS Jupiter (AK-43)|Jupiter]]''\n: 1 [[repair ship]]: ''[[USS Achilles (ARL-41)|Achilles]]''\n: 4 merchant ships\n: 32 [[landing ship, tank|landing ships tank]]\n: 12 [[landing craft infantry]]\n: Escort (Capt. E.A. Solomons)\n:: 4 destroyers\n::: 2 destroyers (both [[Sims class destroyer|Sims-class]]): ''[[USS Mustin (DD-413)|Mustin]]'', ''[[USS Morris (DD-417)|Morris]]''\n::: 2 destroyers (both [[Fletcher class destroyer|Fletcher-class]]: ''[[USS Stevens (DD-479)|Stevens]]'', ''[[USS Howorth|Howorth]]''\n:: 2 frigates (both [[Tacoma class frigate|Tacoma-class]]): ''[[USS Carson City (PF-50)|Carson City]]'', ''[[USS Burlington (PF-51)|Burlington]]''\n\n'''Reinforcement Group Two (Task Group 78.7)'''\n\n[[File:USS_Drayton_%28DD-366%29_underway_at_slow_speed_on_5_August_1936.jpg|220px|thumb|Destroyer ''Drayton'']]\n[[File:USS_Peoria_%28PF-67%29.jpg|220px|thumb|Tacoma-class frigate]]\n\nCaptain J.K.P. Ginder<br>\nArriving 24 October\n: 32 [[landing ship, tank|landing ships tank]]\n: 24 merchant ships\n: Escort (Capt. Ginder)\n:: 4 destroyers (all [[Fletcher class destroyer|Fletcher-class]]): ''[[USS Nicholas (DD-449)|Nicholas]]'', ''[[USS O'Bannon (DD-450)|O'Bannon]]'', ''[[USS Taylor (DD-468)|Taylor]]'', ''[[USS Hopewell (DD-681)|Hopewell]]''\n:: 2 frigates (both [[Tacoma class frigate|Tacoma-class]]): ''[[USS Muskogee|Muskogee]]'', ''[[USS San Pedro|San Pedro]]''\n\n'''Reinforcement Group Three (Task Group 78.9)'''<br>\nCommander J.L. Steinmetz, USCG<br>\nArriving 29 October\n: 62 [[landing ship, tank|landing ships tank]]\n: 19 merchant ships\n: Escort (Capt. W.M. Cole)\n:: 5 destroyers (all [[Mahan class destroyer|Mahan-class]]):  ''[[USS Mahan (DD-364)|Mahan]]'', ''[[USS Drayton (DD-366)|Drayton]]'', ''[[USS Lamson (DD-367)|Lamson]]'', ''[[USS Flusser (DD-368)|Flusser]]'', ''[[USS Smith (DD-378)|Smith]]''\n:: 4 frigates (all [[Tacoma class frigate|Tacoma-class]]): ''[[USS Eugene (PF-40)|Eugene]]'', ''[[USS El Paso (PF-41)|El Paso]]'', ''[[USS Van Buren (PF-42)|Van Buren]]'', ''[[USS Orange|Orange]]''\n\n==== Southern Attack Force (Task Force 79) ====\n{{multiple image\n | direction = horizontal\n | width = 160\n | header = Amphibious force commander for Southern Landing Area\n | image1 = Theodore Wilkinson 1944 small.jpg\n | caption1 = Vice Adm. Theodore S. Wilkinson \n}}\n{{multiple image\n | direction = horizontal\n | width = 220\n | header = Amphibious command ships\n | image1 = USS_Mount_Olympus_(AGC-8)_in_June_1944.jpg\n | caption1 = USS ''Mount Olympus''\n | image2 = USS_Appalachian_(AGC-1)_underway_off_New_York_on_18_October_1943.jpg\n | caption2 = USS ''Appalachian''\n}}\nVice Admiral [[Theodore S. Wilkinson]] in amphibious command ship ''[[USS Mount Olympus|Mount Olympus]]''<br>\nEmbarking [[File:XXIV_Corps_SSI.gif|28px]] '''[[XXIV Corps (United States)|XXIV Army Corps]]'''\n\n'''Attack Group \"Able\" (Task Group 79.1)'''<br>\nRear Admiral R.L. Conolly in amphibious command ship ''[[USS Appalachian|Appalachian]]''<br>\nEmbarking [[File:7th_Infantry_Division_DUI.svg|28px]] [[7th Infantry Division (United States)|7th Infantry \"Bayonet\" Division]] (Left beaches)\n\n: '''Transport Group \"Able\" (Task Group 79.3)'''\n: Capt. C.G. Richardson\n:: Transport Division 7 (Capt. Richardson)\n::: 3 [[attack transport]]s: ''[[USS Cavalier|Cavalier]]'', ''[[USS J. Franklin Bell|J. Franklin Bell]]'', ''[[USS Feland|Feland]]''\n::: 1 [[transport]]: ''Golden City''\n::: 1 [[attack cargo ship]]: ''[[USS Thuban|Thuban]]''\n::: 1 [[landing ship dock]]: ''[[USS Lindenwald|Lindenwald]]''\n:: Transport Division 30 (Capt. C.A. Mission)\n::: 3 [[attack transport]]s: ''[[USS Knox (APA-46)|Knox]]'', ''[[USS Calvert (AP-65)|Calvert]]'', ''[[USS Custer|Custer]]''\n::: 1 evacuation transport: ''[[USS Rixey|Rixey]]''\n::: 1 [[attack cargo ship]]: ''[[USS Chara|Chara]]''\n::: 1 [[landing ship dock]]: ''[[USS Ashland (LSD-1)|Ashland]]''\n:: Transport Division 38 (Capt. Charles Allen)\n::: 3 [[attack transport]]s: ''[[USS Lamar (APA-47)|Lamar]]'', ''[[USS Alpine|Alpine]]'', ''[[USS Heywood|Heywood]]''\n::: 2 [[transport]]s: ''[[USS Starlight|Starlight]]'', ''[[USS Monitor|Monitor]]''\n::: 1 [[attack cargo ship]]s: ''[[USS Alshain|Alshain]]''\n:: Transport Division \"X-Ray\" (Capt. J.A. Snackenberg)\n::: 2 attack transports: ''[[USS George Clymer|George Clymer]]'', ''[[USS President Hayes|President Hayes]]''\n::: 1 cargo ship: ''[[USS Mercury (AK-42)|Mercury]]''\n:: Screen (Capt. W.J. Marshall)\n::: 8 [[Fletcher class destroyer|Fletcher-class]] destroyers (5 x 5-in. main battery): ''[[USS Erben|Erben]]'', ''[[USS Walker (DD-517)|Walker]]'', ''[[USS Hale (DD-642)|Hale]]'', ''[[USS Abbot (DD-629)|Abbot]]'', ''[[USS Black|Black]]'', ''[[USS Chauncey (DD-667)|Chauncey]]'', ''[[USS Braine|Braine]]'', ''[[USS Gansevoort|Gansevoort]]''\n\n'''Attack Group \"Baker\" (Task Group 79.2)'''<br>\nRear Admiral F.B. Royal in amphibious command ship ''[[USS Rocky Mount|Rocky Mount]]''<br>\nEmbarking [[File:96th_Infantry_Division_SSI.svg|28px]] [[96th Infantry Division (United States)|96th Infantry (\"Deadeye\") Division]]  (Right beaches)\n\n[[File:USS_George_F._Elliott_AP-105.jpg|260px|thumb|Transport ''George F. Elliott'']]\n[[File:USS_Capricornus_%28AKA-57%29_underway_at_low_speed_c1945.jpg|260px|thumb|Attack cargo ship ''Capricornus'']