 underway\n | image2 = USS_Portland_(CA-33)_in_a_drydock_at_the_Cockatoo_Island_Dockyard,_circa_in_late_1942_(NH_81992).jpg\n | caption2 = Heavy cruiser ''Portland'' in drydock\n}}\n<!--[[File:USS_Tennessee_BB43.jpg|180px|thumb|Battleship ''Tennessee'']]\nFile:USS_Portland_(CA-33)_in_a_drydock_at_the_Cockatoo_Island_Dockyard,_circa_in_late_1942_(NH_81992).jpg\n[[File:USS_Minneapolis_(CA-36)_in_Puget_Sound_on_27_June_1945_(NH_96702).jpg|180px|thumb|Heavy cruiser ''Minneapolis'']]-->\nRear Admiral [[Jesse B. Oldendorf]] in heavy cruiser ''[[USS Louisville (CA-28)|Louisville]]''\n: '''Battleship Division 2''' (Rear Adm. [[Theodore E. Chandler]])\n:: 3 old battleships: [[USS Tennessee (BB-43)|''Tennessee'']] (Capt. J.B. Heffernan), [[USS California (BB-44)|''California'']] (Capt. H.P. Burnett), [[USS Pennsylvania (BB-38)|''Pennsylvania'']] (Capt. C.F. Martin)\n: '''Cruiser Division 4''' (Rear Adm. Oldendorf)\n:: 3 heavy cruisers: [[USS Louisville (CA-28)|''Louisville'']] (Capt. S.H. Hurt), [[USS Portland (CA-33)|''Portland'']] (Capt. T.G.W. Settle), [[USS Minneapolis (CA-36)|''Minneapolis'']] (Capt. H.B. Slocum)\n: '''Cruiser Division 9''' (Rear Adm. [[Walden L. Ainsworth]])\n:: 1 light cruiser: [[USS Honolulu (CL-48)|''Honolulu'']] (Capt. H.R. Thurber)\n: '''Cruiser Division 12''' (Rear Adm. [[Robert W. Hayler]])\n:: 2 light cruisers: [[USS Denver (CL-58)|''Denver'']] (Capt. A.M. Bledsoe), [[USS Columbia (CL-56)|''Columbia'']] (Capt. M.E. Curts)\n: '''Screen''' (Capt. R.N. Smoot)\n:: 13 destroyers\n::: 11 [[Fletcher class destroyer|Fletcher-class]]: [[USS Leutze (DD-481)|''Leutze'']], [[USS Newcomb (DD-586)|''Newcomb'']], [[USS Bennion (DD-662)|''Bennion'']],  [[USS Heywood L. Edwards|''Heywood L. Edwards'']], [[USS Richard P. Leary|''Richard P. Leary'']], [[USS Robinson (DD-562)|''Robinson'']], [[USS Ross (DD-563)|''Ross'']], [[USS Albert W. Grant|''Albert W. Grant'']], [[USS Bryant|''Bryant'']], [[USS Halford (DD-480)|''Halford'']], [[USS Claxton (DD-571)|''Claxton''