ropshire]]{{ref|county 2|C2}}\n*[[Wiltshire]]{{ref|county 2|C2}}\n{{div col end}}\n|-\n| District(s) gained county functions || 2009 || 4 || \n{{div col|small=no|colwidth=22em}}\n*[[Borough of Bedford|Bedford]]\n*[[Central Bedfordshire]] (new district created)\n*[[Cheshire East]] (new district created)\n*[[Cheshire West and Chester]] (new district created)\n{{div col end}}\n|-\n| District(s) gained county functions || 1998 || 21 || \n{{div col|small=no|colwidth=22em}}\n*[[Blackburn with Darwen]]\n*[[Blackpool]]\n*[[Bracknell Forest]]\n*[[Halton (borough)|Halton]]\n*[[Herefordshire]]{{ref|county 1|C1}} (new district created)\n*[[Medway]] (new district created)\n*[[Nottingham]]\n*[[City of Peterborough|Peterborough]]\n*[[Plymouth]]\n*[[Borough of Reading|Reading]]\n*[[Slough]]\n*[[Southend-on-Sea]]\n*[[Stoke-on-Trent]]\n*[[Borough of Swindon|Swindon]]\n*[[Telford and Wrekin]]\n*[[Thurrock]]\n*[[Torbay]]\n*[[Warrington]]\n*[[West Berkshire]]\n*[[Royal Borough of Windsor and Maidenhead|Windsor and Maidenhead]]\n*[[Wokingham (district)|Wokingham]]\n{{div col end}}\n|-\n| District(s) gained county functions || 1997 || 11 || \n{{div col|small=no|colwidth=22em}}\n*[[Bournemouth (borough)|Bournemouth]]\n*[[Brighton and Hove]] (new district created)\n*[[Derby]]\n*[[Darlington (borough)|Darlington]]\n*[[Leicester]]\n*[[Luton]]\n*[[Borough of Milton Keynes|Milton Keynes]]\n*[[Poole]]\n*[[Portsmouth]]\n*[[Rutland]]{{ref|county 1|C1}}\n*[[Southampton]]\n{{div col end}}\n|-\n| District gained county functions || 1996 || 13 || \n{{div col|small=no|colwidth=22em}}\n*[[Bath and North East Somerset]] (new district created)\n*[[Bristol]]{{ref|county 1|C1}}\n*[[East Riding of Yorkshire]]{{ref|county 2|C2}} (new district created)\n*[[Hartlepool (borough)|Hartlepool]]\n*[[Kingston upon Hull]]\n*[[Middlesbrough (borough)|Middlesbrough]]\n*[[North East Lincolnshire]] (new district created)\n*[[North Lincolnshire]] (new district created)\n*[[North Somerset]]\n*[[Redcar and Cleveland]]\n*[[South Gloucestershire]] (new district created)\n*[[Stockton-on-Tees (borough)|Stockton-on-Tees]]\n*[[York]]\n{{div col end}}\n|-\n| County gained district functions || 1995 || 1 || \n*[[Isle of Wight]]{{ref|county 1|C1}}\n|-\n| Sui generis || 1890 || 1 || \n*[[Isles of Scilly]]\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" | Total || 56 || \n|}\n\n===Civil parishes===\n*[[List of civil parishes in England]]\n\n===Hierarchical list of regions, counties and districts===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Region || Ceremonial county || Metropolitan or<br />non-metropolitan<br />county || Districts, boroughs and cities\n|- style=\"border-top: 3px solid black\"\n| rowspan=\"11\" align=\"center\" |'''[[East of England]]'''<br />[[File:East of England counties 2019 map.jpg|250px]] || rowspan=\"3\" | [[Essex]] || colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #eeffeb\" | '''1'''.&nbsp;[[Thurrock]] U.A. \n|-\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #eeffeb\" | '''2'''.&nbsp;[[Southend-on-Sea]] U.A. \n|-\n| style=\"background: #fff1f1\" | '''3'''.&nbsp;[[Essex County Council|Essex]]&nbsp;\u2020 || style=\"background: #fff7f7\" | ''a'')&nbsp;[[Harlow]], ''b'')&nbsp;[[Epping Forest (district)|Epping Forest]], ''c'')&nbsp;[[Brentwood (borough)|Brentwood]], ''d'')&nbsp;[[Basildon (district)|Basildon]], ''e'')&nbsp;[[Castle Point]], ''f'')&nbsp;[[Rochford (district)|Rochford]], ''g'')&nbsp;[[Maldon District|Maldon]], ''h'')&nbsp;[[Chelmsford (borough)|Chelmsford]], ''i'')&nbsp;[[Uttlesford]], ''j'')&nbsp;[[Braintree (district)|Braintree]], ''k'')&nbsp;[[Colchester (borough)|Colchester]], ''l'')&nbsp;[[Tendring District|Tendring]]\n|-\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #fff1f1\" | '''4'''.&nbsp;[[Hertfordshire]]&nbsp;\u2020 || style=\"background: #fff7f7\" | ''a'')&nbsp;[[Three Rivers, England|Three Rivers]], ''b'')&nbsp;[[Watford]], ''c'')&nbsp;[[Hertsmere]], ''d'')&nbsp;[[Welwyn Hatfield]], ''e'')&nbsp;[[Broxbourne (borough)|Broxbourne]], ''f'')&nbsp;[[East Hertfordshire]], ''g'')&nbsp;[[Stevenage]], ''h'')&nbsp;[[North Hert