artlepool (borough)|Hartlepool]] U.A.\n|- style=\"height: 1em\"<!-- ensure that Stockton-on-Tees cell spans part of Durham as well as North Yorkshire ceremonial counties rows: workaround for Webkit/Chrome rowheight bug, otherwise defaults to 0 (appearing only within North Yorkshire); min-height has no effect -->\n| colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #eeffeb\" | '''6'''.&nbsp;[[Stockton-on-Tees (borough)|Stockton-on-Tees]] U.A.\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[North Yorkshire]]<br /><small>(part only)</small> \n|-\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #eeffeb\" | '''7'''.&nbsp;[[Redcar and Cleveland]] U.A.\n|-\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #eeffeb\" | '''8'''.&nbsp;[[Middlesbrough (borough)|Middlesbrough]] U.A.\n|- style=\"border-top: 3px solid black\"\n| rowspan=\"10\" align=\"center\" |'''[[North West England]]'''<br />[[File:North West England counties 2009 map.svg|200px]] || rowspan=\"4\" | [[Cheshire]] || colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #eeffeb\" | '''1'''.&nbsp;[[Cheshire East]] U.A.\n|-\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #eeffeb\" | '''2'''.&nbsp;[[Cheshire West and Chester]] U.A.\n|-\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #eeffeb\" | '''3'''.&nbsp;[[Halton (borough)|Halton]] U.A.\n|-\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #eeffeb\" | '''4'''.&nbsp;[[Warrington]] U.A.\n|-\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #fff1f1\" | '''5'''.&nbsp;[[Cumbria]]&nbsp;\u2020 || style=\"background: #fff7f7\" | ''a'')&nbsp;[[Barrow-in-Furness (borough)|Barrow-in-Furness]], ''b'')&nbsp;[[South Lakeland]], ''c'')&nbsp;[[Copeland, Cumbria|Copeland]], ''d'')&nbsp;[[Allerdale]], ''e'')&nbsp;[[Eden, Cumbria|Eden]], ''f'')&nbsp;[[City of Carlisle|Carlisle]]\n|-\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #e1f7ff\" | '''6'''.&nbsp;[[Greater Manchester]] * || style=\"background: #f1fbff\" | ''a'')&nbsp;[[Bolton (borough)|Bolton]], ''b'')&nbsp;[[Bury (borough)|Bury]], ''c'')&nbsp;[[Manchester]], ''d'')&nbsp;[[Oldham (borough)|Oldham]], ''e'')&nbsp;[[Rochdale (borough)|Rochdale]], ''f''